        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Fear kite starting at the arena arch and they run down the ramp towards the bank.  When they get to the bottom, back off pet and run to the top again and wait for fear to break.  You won't get any adds even if they run all the way to WL zone as long as you or your pet don't chase them out of the tunnel.  </P><P>Lower arena and bank area can drop robes but be ready to spend about 40 days played doing it.  You'll get about 10 plate BP's in the mean time and might find an MQ robe with the cash/trade.</P><P>At 60 you can single pull everything up to upper arena if I recall.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
